{"tid":973914,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒撚悲歌][環保撚] 今日收工去左大家樂要左杯紅豆冰","createTime":"2019-01-08T13:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T13:34:04.000Z","uid":24061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"05359779998a7bb322ccaa254e0821372f30e1cc","tid":973914,"uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"話說今日收工太肚餓近近地食左個大家樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,咁就豪一豪打算飲杯紅豆冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到攞餐個時見到杯紅豆冰冇比飲筒,嚇到臉都青曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,唔記得左好似係咩新一年全面禁飲筒,<br />\n雖然好似話可以問店員攞飲筒,但頂我毒撚黎呀嘛, 平時小巴都唔敢嗌有落, 邊敢問人攞飲筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 之前睇連登仲要話問攞飲筒會俾人罵番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n咁我最後冇問到啦, 要就咁成杯飲一杯面頭全部都係冰,下層就係紅豆既紅豆冰, 係咁飲到D冰不得止, 仲唔小心跌曬D紅豆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。我真係覺得飲紅豆冰唔俾飲筒真係反人類行為, 但我可以做到既只係係心入臉罵店員千次萬次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後塔小巴番屋企個陣, 一路仲係心入臉罵緊店員既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 唔記得左禁我平時我死都會禁既落車鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 搞到司機MISS左我屋企個站, 我豁左勇氣講左我呢世人第一句: &quot;司機, XX花園有落呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !&quot; 。小巴司機勁燥底回左句: 早D講有落呀嘛, 你X&amp;%)$%()@#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ! 敢怒不敢言既我默默地落左車, 只流下一滴眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 繼續番屋企OT了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環保固然重要,但唔係要我地全香港人都要做埋D反智行為去一刀切就話要環保呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 係香港毒撚多定環保撚多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,我敢講毒撚一定最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 顧得環保撚黎又顧唔到毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 我地邊敢去問店員攞飲筒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,<br />\n依家係連紙飲筒都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 問店員攞又會串你兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 強烈要求回歸以前咁人人有飲筒!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b695cb06ef6c4d922b8a725f3459bbdf9821ac4","tid":973914,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你毒牙"},{"pid":"d9fe052a56c80eb47b69e0641f6bb6143783862e","tid":973914,"uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b695cb06ef6c4d922b8a725f3459bbdf9821ac4","tid":973914,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你毒牙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"毒撚多定環保撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}